{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Console.info()","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/info","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console_API\">Console API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console\"><code>Console</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Métodos</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/assert\"><code>assert()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/clear\"><code>clear()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/count\"><code>count()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/countReset\"><code>countReset()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/debug\"><code>debug()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/dir\"><code>dir()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/dirxml\"><code>dirxml()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/error\"><code>error()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/group\"><code>group()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/groupCollapsed\"><code>groupCollapsed()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/groupEnd\"><code>groupEnd()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/info\"><code>info()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/log\"><code>log()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/profile\"><code>profile()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/profileEnd\"><code>profileEnd()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/table\"><code>table()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/time\"><code>time()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/timeEnd\"><code>timeEnd()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/timeLog\"><code>timeLog()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/timeStamp\"><code>timeStamp()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/trace\"><code>trace()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/warn\"><code>warn()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Páginas relacionadas a Console API</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/console\"><code>Window.console</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/console\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope.console</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"><div class=\"notecard warning\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>Non-standard:</strong> This feature is non-standard and is not on a standards track. Do not use it on production sites facing the Web: it will not work for every user. There may also be large incompatibilities between implementations and the behavior may change in the future.</p></div></div>\n\n<p>Apresenta uma mensagem de saída no&nbsp;console do navegador&nbsp;. No Firefox e Chrome , um pequeno ícone \"i\" e apresentado próximo aos items do log do console .&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect3\">\n  <p><strong>Note:</strong> This feature is available in <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API\">Web Workers</a></p>\n</div><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sintaxe","title":"Sintaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">console.info(<em>obj1</em> [, <em>obj2</em>, ..., <em>objN</em>]);\nconsole.info(<em>msg</em> [, <em>subst1</em>, ..., <em>substN</em>]);\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parâmetros","title":"Parâmetros","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"obj1\"><code>obj1</code> ... <code>objN</code></dt>\n <dd><code>A lista de objetos javascript para saída . As representações de strings de&nbsp;cada um desses objetos são anexados juntos em ordem de listagem e saida .&nbsp;</code></dd>\n <dt id=\"msg\"><code>msg</code></dt>\n <dd><code>Uma string javascript que contém zero ou mais strings para&nbsp;substituição.</code></dd>\n <dt id=\"subst1\"><code>subst1</code> ... <code>substN</code></dt>\n <dd><code>Objeto javascript o qual substitui strings com msg. Isso permite controle adicional sobre o formato da saída.</code></dd>\n</dl>\n\n<p>Veja&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console#outputting_text_to_the_console\">Outputting text to the console</a>&nbsp;na documentação <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console\"><code>console</code></a> para mais &nbsp;detalhes.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificações","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificações</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentários</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://console.spec.whatwg.org/#consoleinfoobject--object-\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Console API<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'console.info()' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Padrão em tempo real</span></td>\n   <td>Definição inicial</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect4\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect5\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Características</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\